# Development Server Control

Before making development edits in this project, stop the frontend and backend dev servers if they are running.

- Check existing terminals or ports before editing.
- Stop `pnpm dev`, Vite, and Django `runserver` processes when code changes are about to begin.
- Restart services only when verification or manual testing needs them.
